content:
Per the main connectathon 29 page track schedules are due today. Unfortunately the Connectathon Session Capture 29 page (where I assume the schedules are to be posted) is missing tracks.

https://confluence.hl7.org/display/FHIR/Connectathon+Session+Capture+29

For example, the "Longitudinal Maternal & Infant Health Information for Research" track is missing.

https://confluence.hl7.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=79517823

Is someone on point to make the session capture page is updated to match the actual tracks?
@Sandra Vance @Josh Mandel
I have the same questions @Sandra Vance when/how do we get tracks onto https://confluence.hl7.org/display/FHIR/Connectathon+Session+Capture+29 ?

Josh Mandel said:

I have the same questions Sandra Vance when/how do we get tracks onto https://confluence.hl7.org/display/FHIR/Connectathon+Session+Capture+29 ?

Hey guys - sorry I missed this message before but all of the tracks have been added to the session capture as of 11/16. If there is one missing please let me k now.
